data.description: Excellent Location… New Roof 1/2024, Beautiful 4 bedroom home with a sparkling in-ground pool right off the Master Bedroom. This Home has so much to offer, Great floor plan, High Ceilings, Open concept for an easy flow… Fridge is included in the Kitchen, updated Paint.  The Back yard boast a large covered deck, Outdoor TV for Sunday Funday, BBQ Pit, storage building, refreshing pool great for entertaining.  Green area on the side yard a for your pets. The Home is in walking distance to the elementary schools, close to shopping and located in Huffman ISD. The subdivision has a private boat launch and park on Lake Houston for the residents. Ask about the Home Warranty…. Call to schedule your appointment today!
